								//First release alpha review:ENG:The coolest & the most realistic fishing game on Steam, but...The game is cheap, but very little content. Game info and ads does can confuse users and the game is not really as big as it looks. The game is really Early Access the game.The game is on the one hand, therefore, difficult to evaluate and write reviews because the game is not really enough significant content, which could be something to say.The game is and looks promising, but the game missing a lot of things, what i like to see in this game. The game is not really any free-form fishing game such as Rapala Pro Fish game, even this game have "Freeroam mode". The game is on the other hand does work, but it should be much more greatly simplify the mechanics of the game, which would be more content and less visual beauty.More than that the game is like most of the cheap games, so on the desktop fish in the fishing game where you fish place.In the game there is only one game mode and one of the really small "pond" fish place and one fish species at this time. The player can not even change the place of the fish pond and walk freely in the environment. The game does not include a lake or sea fishing or even a motor boat rides.Also fish in artificial intelligence does not seem to be very good or even the environment seems to be enough interaction or vitalization and the environment there is not much else in life.The player can not change the gear or fishing supplies and the game will also be maybe possible to include additional content later on a charge even though the game may not be worth it.The game is missing a second over the fishing feeling, because the fishing area seems like it would be an empty place, and the game area seem plausible. In the game there is no other artificial intelligence fishermen, which would be a nice addition to the game, so the player is quite lonely when the game is also not have a multiplayer game mode.It is, frankly, this is a lightweight desktop fishing game. The game run the same as ice fishing or angling fishing, so this is not a hardcore fishing game.Sad to say also, that even the cat could cry this game, because the cat would not be able to fish the cats do not have enough fish to offer. x3I fear only that the game is going to be a long time Early Access the game, even years. Very few of the game is not over yet reached the level of the Early Acces. So the game can stay many players short-lived.I can recommend the game, but I would recommend the game actually later if the game actually add more content. :3//EnsimmÃ¤inen alpha julkaisu version arvostelu:FIN:TyylikkÃ¤in ja realistisin kalastuspeli Steamissa, mutta...Peli on halpa, mutta todella vÃ¤hÃ¤n sisÃ¤ltÃ¶Ã¤. Pelin esittely ja mainokset hÃ¤mÃ¤Ã¤vÃ¤t kÃ¤yttÃ¤jÃ¤Ã¤, eikÃ¤ peli ole oikeastaan niin iso kuin miltÃ¤ nÃ¤yttÃ¤Ã¤. Peli on siis todella Early Acces peli.PelissÃ¤ on siis toisaalta vaikea arvioida ja kirjoittaa arvostelua, koska pelissÃ¤ ei ole oikeastaan riittÃ¤vÃ¤sti merkittÃ¤vÃ¤Ã¤ sisÃ¤ltÃ¶Ã¤, josta voisi jotakin sanoa.Peli on ja nÃ¤yttÃ¤Ã¤ lupaavalta, mutta pelistÃ¤ puuttuu todella paljon asioita vielÃ¤, mitÃ¤ itse haluasin nÃ¤hdÃ¤ pelissÃ¤ olevan. Peli ei varsinaisesti ole mikÃ¤Ã¤n vapaa muotoinen kalastus peli kuten Rapala Pro Fish -peli. Peli on toisaalta ihan toimiva, mutta pitÃ¤isi paljon enemmÃ¤n huomattavasti yksinkertaisemmasta peli mekaniikasta, jossa olisi enemmÃ¤n sisÃ¤ltÃ¶Ã¤ ja vÃ¤hemmÃ¤n visuaalista kauneutta.EnemmÃ¤nkin peli on kuten useimmat halvat pelit niin, tyÃ¶pÃ¶dÃ¤ltÃ¤ kalastettava kalastus peli, jossa kalastetaan paikaltaan.PelissÃ¤ ei ole kuin yksi peli muoto oikeastaan ja yksi pieni "lampi" kalapaikka sekÃ¤ yksi kala laji tÃ¤llÃ¤hetkellÃ¤. Pelaaja ei pysty myÃ¶skÃ¤Ã¤n vaihtamaan kala paikkaa lammella, eikÃ¤ kÃ¤velemÃ¤Ã¤n vapaasti ympÃ¤ristÃ¶ssÃ¤. Peli ei siis sisÃ¤llÃ¤ jÃ¤rvi tai meri kalastusta tai vaikkapa moottori veneellÃ¤ ajelua.Pelaaja ei voi myÃ¶skÃ¤Ã¤n vaihtaa asusteita tai kalastustarvikkeita ja peli